@SG_CPP_CLASS SGRVertexBufferObject
@SG_SHORT_DESCRP GPU side vertex buffer object
@SG_LONG_DESCRP SGRVertexBufferObject is used by @SG_FINDREP_RENDERER renderers to store vertex buffer objects on the GPU.
@SG_IMPLE @SG_FINDREP_RENDERER internally uses QRhi.
@SG_FUNC SGRVertexBufferObject(SGRBaseRenderer* renderControl, int bufferSize);
Creates a SGRVertexBufferObject with a size of $bufferSize bytes associated to the @SG_FINDREP_RENDERER renderer $renderControl.
@SG_WARN Negative $bufferSize is undefined behaviour.
@SG_WARN Passing nullptr to $renderControl is undefined behaviour.
